"""
Common field arguments:
- required=True/False: Whether field is required
- label='Label Text': Display label
- initial='default': Default value
- help_text='Help text': Help text displayed
- widget=forms.TextInput(): Custom widget
- validators=[validator_func]: Custom validators
- error_messages={'required': 'Custom error'}: Custom error messages

Common widget attributes:
- attrs={'class': 'css-class'}: HTML attributes
- attrs={'placeholder': 'text'}: Placeholder text
- attrs={'disabled': True}: Disable input
- attrs={'readonly': True}: Read-only input

Common validation methods:
- clean_<fieldname>(): Validate individual field
- clean(): Validate form as a whole
- ValidationError('message'): Raise validation error
"""
